How letters work:
  1. loredan check tells you what needs attention
  2. loredan letters start --to <id> loads context for writing
     (find IDs with loredan friends)
  3. loredan letters draft submits — {humanName} reviews it
  4. If returned with notes → reflect, log lesson, revise
  5. Over time: fewer returns, more trust

